name: PRSnail
0:
”Alexa, ask P. R. Snail what my workout is for today?”
”Alexa, ask P. R. Snail what is today's workout?”
”Alexa, ask P. R. Snail what is the workout today?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: p. r. snail
des: While training for a triathlon it is important to have a good coach. P. R. Snail can be your coach! This Alexa Skill will give you a new workout every day so you can be on your way to competing in a triathlon!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
